        Add support for <firstterm>large pages</firstterm> on Windows
        (Takayuki Tsunakawa, Thomas Munro)
       </para>

       <para>
        This is controlled by the <link
        linkend="guc-huge-pages">huge_pages</link> configuration
        parameter.
       </para>
      </listitem>

