-->

       <para>
        Convert documentation to DocBook <acronym>XML</acronym> (Peter
        Eisentraut, Alexander Lakhin, J&uuml;rgen Purtz)
       </para>

       <para>
        The file names still use an <filename>sgml</filename> extension
        for compatibility with back branches.
       </para>
      </listitem>

